For those of you who consider this a dead horse, my apologies.<br>
<br>
Sarhea and I have spent the last few weeks working on a project.  A roleplay community within FV.  Perhaps you've read about it in the Hero Heart Tavern forum.  Perhaps you've visited the EZBoard we have set up.  Perhaps you've even posted there.<br>
<br>
